News.page_title: The Daggers in Partnership with Johnstone's Paints
News.URL_keywords: The Daggers in Partnership with Johnstone's Paints
News.short_description: Johnstone's Paints are now offering Daggers fans 25% off in store
News.description:
The Daggers are now in partnership with Johnstone's Paints. Johnstone's will be offering Â£50 vouchers as a second prize in our 50/50 draws for the rest of the games this season.

The second prize will start from this Saturday's National League fixture against Solihull Moors and run through the entirety of the rest of the season.

Johnstone's are also offering 25% off for Daggers fans in their stores, take your season ticket or ticket stub into a Johnstone's decorating centre to claim your discount. Find your local store below:
